      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="After types of work are determined and rates are agreed upon, planned distributions and assessments are processed.  These are cost allocations for cross functional work between business units and programs. This is a final step in planning to allow for a complete and accurate roll-up of costs prior to reconciliation, reporting, and budgeting."/>
